Thomas Mapfumo, popularly known as Mukanya, landed in the country to a heroes welcome after 14 years in exile in the United States. He fled the Robert Mugabe regime that sought to jail him over his political views. Mapfumo is set to grace the stage with legendary musician Oliver MtukudziÂ  and Jah Prayzah in a sold out concert in Harare on the 28th of April.